description:
In this Minecraft episode we have some fun with the cool features of Thaumcraft and just do some random experimenting.

MindCrack FTB is a modded Minecraft server Guude has setup for the MindCrackers. It is a private (whitelisted) server. We are currently not accepting applications.

FTB: http://feed-the-beast.com/
MindCrack: http://www.youtube.com/user/MindCrackNetwork
